#ROOMS
#80476
Name A Path To The Estate~
Desc Well trimmed shrubs and bushes line the cobblestone walkway leading up to 
the estate. Small animals scurry through the bushes, looking for a place to 
hide as people enter and leave. A narrow white picket fence lines the 
property, giving a quaint setting in which to live. A big pond rests off the 
walkway to the east, filled with all sorts of freshwater fish. 
~
RoomFlags no_mob indoors~
Room2Flags freshwater_fish~
Sector inside~
Exit north 80477
Exit southwest 54692
End


#80477
Name The Front Door~
Desc Approaching the door, the well-done stone work to the house can be done.  
Intricately laid out stones, perfect in spacing, comprise the foundation in 
walls. It is completed by a slanting stone roof, which appears quite sturdy 
in nature. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit north 80478
EFlags door closed locked nopass infuriating~
EKeyvnum 80480
Exit south 80476
End


#80478
Name The Living Room~
Desc A fine polished marble lines the walls of the living room, glistening in any 
bit of ambient light that may reflect off of it. Solid onyx chairs line the 
room, adorned by layered multi-colored tiles in the table, inset with the 
name of the owner. Sturdy torches hang next to the entranceways, providing 
quite a bit of light to the surrounding area. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit north 80481
Exit east 80479
Exit south 80477
EFlags door closed locked nopass infuriating~
EKeyvnum 80480
Exit west 80480
End


#80479
Name The Kitchen~
Desc An old wrought iron potbelly stove rests against the east wall with a 
makeshift vent going through the exterior wall for ventilation. Scattered 
about the kitchen are a few cupboards, housing various cooking items and 
items required to prepare food. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit west 80478
End


#80480
Name Storage Room~
Desc A makeshift storage room lies here, with items scattered about..almost like 
a closet, but not really storing anything that a closet would. Various items 
many years older than the owner himself lie scattered about on the floor, 
most of them collecting dust. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit east 80478
End


#80481
Name A Wide Hallway~
Desc A small hallway stretches north from the living room, branching off into 
various other rooms.  More torches hang near the doorways, used to ensure 
that those who stumble around when half-asleep don't run into things. Extra 
wide doorways are utilized, more than adequate for a full grown dragon to 
pass through with their wings tucked in. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit north 80484
Exit east 80483
Exit south 80478
Exit west 80482
End


#80482
Name The Master Bedroom~
Desc Sandstone portraits of Drux and his old friends layer the walls in this 
bedroom.  A gigantic bed is resting in the middle of it, with weapons racks 
near the window to the west. A small rack of clerical supplies rests against 
the north wall, holding everything from pens to empty scrolls and guides to 
reference as required. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit east 80481
End


#80483
