and bed lay about the room.  The bed angles to the northeast, with beautiful 
hand-made bedspreads covering it. A few pictures of friends long since 
fallen depict vicious war scenes from the times of the Roving Guard. 
~
RoomFlags indoors~
Sector inside~
Exit west 80481
End


